name: RestaurantRoulette
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: restaurant roulette
des: Restaurant Roulette is a simple but useful app that can help you decide on a place to eat. All you have to do is tell it what restaurants you're considering or craving, and it will randomly generate a restaurant name based on the choices you're considering.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
